<p>I have two camel routes that are connected via a direct: link, not linked via JMS-Queue in this case.</p>  <p>Can I have a transaction between these two routes?</p>  <p>e.g.</p>  <pre><code>&lt;route id="fileRoute"&gt;    ..    &lt;to uri="direct:start"&gt; &lt;/route&gt;  &lt;route id="directStartRoute"&gt;    &lt;from uri="direct:start"&gt;    &lt;to uri="http://myhost/mypath"&gt; &lt;/route&gt; </code></pre>